# Government Tender Announcement

## Title (English) / Titre (Français)

* TBIPS - Business Transformation Architect and Database Modeller/Information Management Modeller
* Architecte de transformation des activités et Modélisateur de données/Modélisateur en Gestion de l'information

## Document Reference

* Reference Number: PW-23-01024281
* Amendment Number: 1
* Solicitation Number: N23-19882
* Publication Date: 2023-02-01
* Tender Closing Date: 2023-03-01T14:00:00
* Amendment Date: 2023-02-10

## Tender Details

* Expected Contract Start Date: None
* Expected Contract End Date: None
* Tender Status (English): Expired
* Tender Status (Français): Expiré
* Goods and Services Classification Code (GSIN): D302A
* GSIN Description (English): Informatics Professional Services
* GSIN Description (Français): Services professionnels, informatique
* UNSPSC: None
* UNSPSC Description (English): None
* UNSPSC Description (Français): None
* Procurement Category: SRV
* Notice Type (English): Request for Proposal
* Notice Type (Français): Demande de propositions
* Procurement Method (English): Competitive - Selective Tendering
* Procurement Method (Français): Concurrentielle - Appel d'offres sélectif

## Contract at Work

This procurement is set aside under the federal government Procurement Strategy for Indigenous Business (PSIB) and offers an opportunity for Indigenous businesses to participate.

The objective of this contract is to provide high-level expertise data analytic services to develop and deploy multiple programs as identified below:

* Data Governance
* Strategic Data Management
* Data Science
* Business Intelligence

## Eligibility Criteria

This tender is open to eligible bidders that meet the requirements specified in the solicitation.

## Submission Requirements

Please submit your proposal in accordance with the instructions outlined in the solicitation.

## Contracting Entity and Point of Contact

* Contracting Entity: Natural Sciences and Engineering Research Council of Canada
* Address: 350 Albert Street, Ottawa, Ontario, K1A 1H5, Canada
* Point of Contact: Bennett, Tamara
* Email: tenders@nserc-crsng.gc.ca
* Phone: None
* Fax:
